Set Up
======

To use:
1. git clone <remote git project location>.git vim
2. git submodule update --init
3. ln -s /<full path>/vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc
4. ln -s /<full path>/vim/.vim ~/.vim
5. mkdir ~/.vim_backup

The vim set up should be generic for all platforms. Tested with vim, gVim, and MacVim.

Update Plugins
=================

Plugins are managed using [Pathogen](https://github.com/tpope/vim-pathogen). The
plugins are referenced as git submodules in the bundle directory.

To update all submodules:
git submodule foreach git pull

